data.description: Meticulously maintained home in Washington Township.  From the front entry you are greeted by wood flooring throughout and a neutral pallet.  To your left, a generously sized front living room that continues into the dining room.  Then, a large open kitchen with new cabinets and granite counters.  Bar seating in kitchen and room for a kitchen table allows for entertaining with ease.  Kitchen is truly the heart of the home here with access to the second living room with large fireplace to enjoy quality time with family and friends.  Half bath and the laundry room complete the first floor.  Upstairs you will find 4 large bedrooms and a newly renovated full bathroom.  The basement has been partially finished ready for the finishing touches.  This home is on an over-sized corner lot that has a large fenced yard ready for running and playing or for your furry friend to enjoy!  Make your appointment early, you wont want to miss this home!
